<br />
<br />I would most likely be using a heavily-tweaked Windows XP.
<br />
<br />S-video and RCA outputs are important to me. 
<br />
<br />I would go so far as to say HDMI, and turn it into a media centre, but I am not aware of any mini ITX board with that capability as of time of writing
<br />
<br />However -  For emulation, as which would be the main focus of said machine, I believe the boards you have presented to be an excellent start. 
